net.jforum.util.preferences

Class ConfigKeys

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.jforum.util.preferences.ConfigKeys

  • public class ConfigKeys
extends Object
    Encapsulate all configuration keys in constants. This is more typesafe and provides a nice overview of all configuration keys. Last but not least this lets us autocomplete configuration keys under eclipse ;-)
    Author:
    Pieter Olivier
